thread.title: Gail Hughes
thread.title_full: Sheenco Travel reviewed by Gail Hughes

author: Gail Hughes
title: Gail Hughes
text:
My husband and I experienced the majesty of Ireland in 2014. It was truly a trip of a lifetime! Genevieve made the plans for our castle tour and it was so fabulous!! Every stay was unique and beautiful and fun!
My absolute favorite thing was the hawk walk at Ashford Castle!! Never even dreamed of doing something like that! I have memories of a lifetime from that awesome trip and will be forever grateful to Genevieve for making out 14 trip the best we have ever had!!
